Name: HIGHBLAST
About the game: HIGHBLAST is a parkour FPS game partly inspired by games like Redmatch 2 and Karlson. Some of the core mechanics include things like slow motion, time freeze, jetpacks and grappling. Your goal is to destroy the evil enemy robots and escape the levels Hope you have fun! :) Abilities: - Slow Motion - Jetpack - Double Jump - Time Freeze - Wrist Grapple
